Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦助的小鸟不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离巢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经长成大鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a safe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君真坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦率？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真庆幸初次登台的对手是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要练习一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想用一下厕所…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班的小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说今早也在禁断的行星赏鸟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁断的行星？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是男厕所啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男厕所赏鸟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人小弟在学艺会上要亲亲的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和子妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君太受欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野只是像对乌鸦和副部长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我取乐而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受欢迎啊 拓人小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不懂女人心啊 拓人小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 和子妹妹那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤少爷可怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你有两个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能当我画画的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你绝对应该当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是命运了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为此而生的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第一队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「国王」的代表之座还为你空着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们随时准备迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是准备在这里使用王之柱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神赐予的才能 必然是有意义的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有战士之印也就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有强大的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说野心也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士的驭星者没有人能赢得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你胸前刻下的并非战士之印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是王之印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个银河美少年即将被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒没打算取他性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也视他为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤野？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你借点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…听阿姨说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和平时一样说些开心的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是水野喜欢的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦助的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鸦助还喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是那个副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比副部长还喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君的确是很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道鞠野也对拓人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都是水野的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我就不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代的驭星者总算齐聚一堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果人面狮一次都没来过这间房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她使用Ayingott之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她说没找到是说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长说谎的女孩子 真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动之后还被叫出来习武
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是太过分了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚气势不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能挤下三个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子选个喜欢的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下次练习是打赌赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打赌赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟和子的婚约就一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后你可以进她的伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该从哪儿吐槽好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个玩笑 我可当真了哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈你个头啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君对和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的话是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假的话 至少告诉我一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你巫女的身份被谁发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是感觉不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能瞒多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言说通 就会成为真实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 谎言编造的世界是虚幻的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22\b0\fsp0\fs18}（注：参见本片第10话）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实就是不会消逝的虚幻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吧 水野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家吧 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1\b0\fad(0,500)}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如 见见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分开再分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是面对面说清楚比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是不是真的抛弃了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能继续前行不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也想见见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说「其实」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么鞠野会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出姐姐的架子 说些自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人 为什么现在又回到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摆出姐姐的架子 说些自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因为她回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚捞的蝾螺 要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的我有些古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想到她也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的快疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她在岛上的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等那个人离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另附
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来是第一次去本土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么点小激动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚捞的蝾螺 要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是预知梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去本土购物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能载我去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆搭讪 最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 第一次去本土？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全驾驶 加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 暖暖手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再握一次我的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子现在 真的在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上起 岛上的空气就在躁动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试离开岛上了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…和子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是净身的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女的职责？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说今晨开始结界躁动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是些粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是日死之巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没尝试过离开岛上是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子是巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 也离不开岛上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有 巫女的职责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上的四方巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守口如瓶 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来我们这儿商量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:47.54,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}喜欢这翠色的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:54.36,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}风又带来夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:57.42,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}千回辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.39,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur4}万回闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:05.50,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光就这样诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开岛上的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日死之巫女同学
Comment: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:23:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有我必须做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你是日死之巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人之印
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊吧 驯化！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------


